The clock tower looks to be about tall enough to reach the third floor of the school. [p]
At its base, there is a small door about big enough for an adult to enter while bent down.[p]
The door solemnly opened.[p]
After opening, the door seems to beckon the one standing in front of it to enter with an irresistible mental energy.[p]
I cannot resist that power.[p]
As I enter, the door closes with a hopeless thunder.[p]


